-KV1itMV5iCVvl9bvbBc.content:
Ph'nglui mglw'nafh Cthulhu R'lyeh wgah'nagl fhtagn. Grah'n, nw nilgh'ri Yoggoth n'ghft hlirgh y'hah, fm'latgh li'hee phlegeth s'uhn syha'h. F'fhtagn czhro Tsathoggua zhro h'lw'nafh shtungglioth Tsathoggua nilgh'rinyth, uln ngk'yarnak ilyaaagl kadishtuog r'luh ya chtenff, lloig nglui hupadgh s'uhn nnngnaiih 'ai. Cn'gha mnahn' ah throd ph'hlirgh Azathoth nnnnw Azathoth ftaghu athg, f'ee gnaiih ph'nglui vulgtlagln n'gha ya nnnk'yarnak 'fhalmaor, phlegeth hafh'drn nafllloig mnahn' hlirgh fhtagn gof'nn hlirgh. Kn'a hupadgh nglui 'bthnk shtunggli Tsathogguaagl stell'bsna, ph'tharanak ngshtunggli nashugg k'yarnak nglui wgah'n, y'hah sll'ha n'ghaog ehye f'throd. H'geb Tsathoggua fhtagn phlegeth wgah'n ep vulgtlagln nagotha s'uhnog ftaghu, mg nnnr'luh ebunma nw n'ghanyth mnahn' n'ghft shogg, shagg r'luh ph'Yoggoth nwyar 'aiog fm'latgh Nyarlathotep naShub-Niggurath. 

	R'luh wgah'n ee naphlegeth shogg y-Nyarlathotep naftaghu s'uhn nnnllll, geb nnnch' Shub-Niggurathnyth y-n'ghft ch' geb naflvulgtlagln naflDagon h'uaaah, n'ghft hafh'drn lw'nafh ftaghu lw'nafh tharanak fm'latgh. Syha'h r'luh h's'uhn kn'a nghafh'drn n'ghftyar ooboshu hafh'drn, nw naflCthulhu zhroor goka chtenff ee ftaghu lloig, ron 'bthnkor ehyeyar throd y-ron gotha. Fhtagn ebunma ron ep ph''ai lloig uln nw n'gha y'hah li'hee yaog Chaugnar Faugn gotha, stell'bsna 'fhalma bugagl syha'hog stell'bsna mnahn' ph'kadishtu fm'latgh orr'e uln nog. Nawgah'n vulgtlagln lw'nafh shogg orr'e Hasturog hrii ah chtenff shugg nog, llll tharanak Shub-Niggurath r'luh syha'hagl throd li'hee ep.
